title: Epstein List Released
author: VD
content_html:
The court has reportedly released a document with 40 attachments. 4chan is already working on compiling the list. The first few things I’ve seen just look like old stuff that we already knew, though.

UPDATE: Nothing new, as far as I have seen. Bill Clinton, Prince Andrew, Leslie Wexner, etc. It looks like yet another controlled release meant to protect the politicians involved.
